1
00:01:37,840 --> 00:01:41,060
[The Epoch of Miyu]

2
00:01:41,120 --> 00:01:43,960
[Episode 36]

3
00:01:51,539 --> 00:01:52,120
Those two people

4
00:01:52,120 --> 00:01:55,380
are probably going to
fight it out in the sales department.

5
00:01:55,960 --> 00:01:57,740
Luckily, it has nothing to do
with our department.

6
00:01:57,740 --> 00:02:00,200
How come
they're not afraid to say anything?

7
00:02:00,390 --> 00:02:01,240
Listen.

8
00:02:01,790 --> 00:02:03,840
Now that
he has done something like this today,

9
00:02:03,840 --> 00:02:05,200
everyone in the meeting room

10
00:02:05,200 --> 00:02:07,060
knows exactly what he wants to do.

11
00:02:07,310 --> 00:02:08,430
When did Lu Zhenzhen

12
00:02:08,430 --> 00:02:10,160
get connected with Wei Siyuan?

13
00:02:11,450 --> 00:02:12,960
Between the vice director and the manager,

14
00:02:12,960 --> 00:02:15,210
there's just a difference in the titles.

15
00:02:15,210 --> 00:02:17,180
If Wei Siyuan wants it,
just let him have it.

16
00:02:17,180 --> 00:02:18,150
Tell Meng Jie

17
00:02:18,170 --> 00:02:20,480
Xu Miyu is the person
in charge of the bidding meeting,

18
00:02:20,480 --> 00:02:22,260
and all implementation details
must be checked by her.

19
00:02:22,260 --> 00:02:24,030
Don't let Lu Zhenzhen interfere.

20
00:02:24,030 --> 00:02:26,170
Leave the rest to Meng Jie
to handle by herself.

21
00:02:26,170 --> 00:02:27,510
She's quite experienced in the workplace.

22
00:02:27,510 --> 00:02:28,910
She knows the best how to deal with it.

23
00:02:28,910 --> 00:02:30,270
Okay. I'll tell her.

24
00:02:30,670 --> 00:02:31,360
Also,

25
00:02:32,240 --> 00:02:33,210
tell Miyu

26
00:02:34,010 --> 00:02:34,910
to be careful with everything.

27
00:02:34,910 --> 00:02:37,910
So the issues between you two
haven't been solved yet?

28
00:02:56,710 --> 00:02:58,570
Mr. Wei, what are your plans next?

29
00:03:00,300 --> 00:03:01,760
Now Ji Feng

30
00:03:01,780 --> 00:03:03,160
is clearly betting everything

31
00:03:03,160 --> 00:03:05,500
on the bidding meeting.

32
00:03:05,530 --> 00:03:08,330
And this time,
the sales department is the main focus.

33
00:03:08,330 --> 00:03:09,840
At this critical juncture,

34
00:03:09,840 --> 00:03:11,800
if he dares to use a newbie,

35
00:03:11,820 --> 00:03:13,220
then he'd better be prepared to fail.

36
00:03:13,220 --> 00:03:14,370
Don't forget that

37
00:03:14,800 --> 00:03:17,030
Xu Miyu is still in the sales department.

38
00:03:17,030 --> 00:03:17,840
That's right.

39
00:03:18,840 --> 00:03:20,190
So what's your plan?

40
00:03:20,780 --> 00:03:21,890
There's no rush.

41
00:03:23,520 --> 00:03:25,320
They are on high alert right now.

42
00:03:25,910 --> 00:03:28,560
When all the bidding companies
have checked in,

43
00:03:28,560 --> 00:03:30,610
and they're so busy receiving the guests,

44
00:03:30,610 --> 00:03:31,960
won't our chance come?

45
00:03:39,460 --> 00:03:41,670
Mr. Wei, I know that although this time,

46
00:03:41,690 --> 00:03:44,180
you only gave me
the position of vice director,

47
00:03:44,180 --> 00:03:46,640
you showed me a lot of respect
at the meeting.

48
00:03:47,020 --> 00:03:49,440
I will definitely find a way to help you.

49
00:04:00,280 --> 00:04:01,080
Miyu.

50
00:04:06,970 --> 00:04:07,960
Why are you here?

51
00:04:07,990 --> 00:04:09,050
What's the matter?

52
00:04:12,430 --> 00:04:13,280
Miyu.

53
00:04:14,520 --> 00:04:15,890
Our whole family

54
00:04:16,720 --> 00:04:18,160
has let you down.

55
00:04:20,510 --> 00:04:22,240
Don't talk about these things.

56
00:04:22,400 --> 00:04:24,380
What's the matter exactly?

57
00:04:25,930 --> 00:04:26,890
Yucheng...

58
00:04:28,870 --> 00:04:30,160
is sick.

59
00:04:30,890 --> 00:04:31,720
I know.

60
00:04:35,510 --> 00:04:37,440
He has undergone a major operation

61
00:04:38,390 --> 00:04:40,450
and several rounds of chemotherapy.

62
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:42,240
Now suddenly,

63
00:04:44,890 --> 00:04:47,320
he wants to give up the treatment.

64
00:04:47,170 --> 00:04:51,930
[Welcome to Purong Hotel]

65
00:04:47,560 --> 00:04:48,360
He refuses to take his medicine.

66
00:04:48,360 --> 00:04:49,690
Nor is he willing to eat.

67
00:04:50,150 --> 00:04:52,050
He also refuses to
let the nurses give him IVs.

68
00:04:52,050 --> 00:04:55,250
No matter how I tried to persuade him,
he wouldn't listen.

69
00:04:55,360 --> 00:04:57,370
This is such a precious human life.

70
00:04:57,570 --> 00:04:59,780
Why doesn't he want to stay alive?

71
00:05:07,440 --> 00:05:08,310
Miyu.

72
00:05:09,440 --> 00:05:10,910
I beg you.

73
00:05:10,930 --> 00:05:12,510
Please go persuade him.

74
00:05:12,950 --> 00:05:14,350
He always listens to you.

75
00:05:14,660 --> 00:05:16,320
You are the one he loves the most.

76
00:05:16,320 --> 00:05:17,720
If it weren't for that...

77
00:05:25,270 --> 00:05:27,270
For the sake of your past marriage,

78
00:05:28,830 --> 00:05:30,430
please help him out

79
00:05:31,270 --> 00:05:33,120
and persuade him to keep living.

80
00:05:36,720 --> 00:05:37,600
I'm sorry.

81
00:05:40,840 --> 00:05:43,250
My relationship with Nie Yucheng is over.

82
00:05:44,210 --> 00:05:46,470
I don't want to disturb his life anymore.

83
00:05:47,800 --> 00:05:48,990
Besides,

84
00:05:49,270 --> 00:05:52,040
what he needs the most right now
is inner peace,

85
00:05:52,870 --> 00:05:55,000
not another emotional entanglement.

86
00:05:56,140 --> 00:06:05,370
[Inpatient Building]

87
00:05:56,940 --> 00:05:57,690
If

88
00:05:57,720 --> 00:05:59,500
you really want to persuade him,

89
00:05:59,500 --> 00:06:00,620
you can tell him

90
00:06:00,650 --> 00:06:01,510
in this world,

91
00:06:01,510 --> 00:06:03,430
there are more important things
than his despair

92
00:06:03,430 --> 00:06:04,890
that he needs to shoulder.

93
00:06:05,520 --> 00:06:06,560
His family,

94
00:06:06,860 --> 00:06:07,820
parents

95
00:06:08,310 --> 00:06:09,220
and child.

96
00:06:10,310 --> 00:06:11,080
I think

97
00:06:11,420 --> 00:06:13,220
he can definitely figure it out.

98
00:06:18,750 --> 00:06:22,550
[North Entrance]

99
00:06:35,080 --> 00:06:36,090
Miyu.

100
00:07:02,680 --> 00:07:04,430
♪ A flicker of dim light ♪

101
00:07:06,190 --> 00:07:07,760
♪ A bowl of warm soup ♪

102
00:07:10,040 --> 00:07:11,820
♪ People in the city ♪

103
00:07:12,780 --> 00:07:15,720
♪ Squeezing into the hustle and bustle ♪

104
00:07:17,650 --> 00:07:19,460
♪ The palms of time ♪

105
00:07:21,380 --> 00:07:24,420
♪ Grinding away the simple days ♪

106
00:07:25,110 --> 00:07:27,640
♪ Sprinkling them into this busy world ♪

107
00:07:29,050 --> 00:07:31,220
♪ To be tasted, bit by bit ♪

108
00:07:32,810 --> 00:07:35,860
♪ Embracing this radiant world ♪

109
00:07:32,880 --> 00:07:34,040
Bear it for a moment.

110
00:07:35,520 --> 00:07:36,520
My husband

111
00:07:36,340 --> 00:07:39,370
♪ Keeps the heart from fading to grey ♪

112
00:07:36,540 --> 00:07:39,940
is the most handsome,
even more handsome than an Arab prince.

113
00:07:39,960 --> 00:07:43,080
♪ Life's joy, sorrow, cold, and warmth ♪

114
00:07:43,820 --> 00:07:46,440
♪ Intertwined within the mundane ♪

115
00:07:47,860 --> 00:07:51,050
♪ Let us bravely gather up ♪

116
00:07:51,720 --> 00:07:55,170
♪ The forgotten past ♪

117
00:07:54,500 --> 00:07:55,810
From now on,

118
00:07:56,080 --> 00:07:58,350
♪ There may be regrets ♪

119
00:07:56,650 --> 00:07:58,650
I won't let you get hurt.

120
00:07:59,100 --> 00:08:00,720
I'll protect you forever.

121
00:08:00,010 --> 00:08:02,190
♪ There may be loneliness ♪

122
00:08:02,000 --> 00:08:04,060
And I'll protect our family forever.

123
00:08:06,080 --> 00:08:07,350
I swear.

124
00:08:13,920 --> 00:08:15,240
Nurse.

125
00:08:17,650 --> 00:08:18,830
I want to eat.

126
00:08:32,299 --> 00:08:35,780
♪ Embracing this radiant world ♪

127
00:08:36,200 --> 00:08:39,320
♪ Keeps the heart from fading to grey ♪

128
00:08:39,200 --> 00:08:40,409
Hello, Mr. Su.

129
00:08:39,809 --> 00:08:43,130
♪ Life's joy, sorrow, cold, and warmth ♪

130
00:08:40,440 --> 00:08:42,130
The verdict is out.

131
00:08:42,159 --> 00:08:43,270
We won the case.

132
00:08:43,669 --> 00:08:46,310
♪ Intertwined within the mundane ♪

133
00:08:47,710 --> 00:08:51,010
♪ Let us bravely gather up ♪

134
00:08:47,990 --> 00:08:49,310
Thanks for your hard work, Mr. Su.

135
00:08:49,310 --> 00:08:50,460
But there's a situation.

136
00:08:50,460 --> 00:08:51,940
You need to be mentally prepared first.

137
00:08:51,580 --> 00:08:55,000
♪ The forgotten past ♪

138
00:08:51,960 --> 00:08:54,010
Mr. Nie has said that

139
00:08:54,080 --> 00:08:56,240
he can't come up with that much money
for the time being.

140
00:08:56,240 --> 00:08:57,650
He has applied for a stay of execution.

141
00:08:57,650 --> 00:08:58,570
I got it.

142
00:08:57,840 --> 00:09:00,510
♪ Walking through this world ♪

143
00:08:59,840 --> 00:09:02,230
Let him
get through this difficult time first.

144
00:09:02,230 --> 00:09:06,340
♪ Leaving no regrets behind ♪

145
00:09:02,640 --> 00:09:04,310
I'm not in a hurry to use this money.

146
00:09:04,310 --> 00:09:05,310
Understood.

147
00:09:06,290 --> 00:09:07,600
Thank you so much

148
00:09:07,620 --> 00:09:09,310
for this period of time, Mr. Su.

149
00:09:09,310 --> 00:09:10,880
You're welcome.

150
00:09:10,910 --> 00:09:12,710
I'm glad my client is satisfied.

151
00:09:38,490 --> 00:09:41,760
[Budget Sheet
of Yuntian Group Bidding Meeting]

152
00:09:41,790 --> 00:09:46,920
[Marketing Campaign Expenses]
[Advertising Fees] [Other Items]

153
00:09:50,600 --> 00:09:53,570
[Signature of the Person in Charge,
Ji Feng]

154
00:10:02,350 --> 00:10:04,110
Are you still at the hotel?

155
00:10:04,200 --> 00:10:04,540
[Release to send]

156
00:10:04,690 --> 00:10:06,130
[Xu Miyu]

157
00:10:06,150 --> 00:10:07,200
[Typing...]

158
00:10:09,960 --> 00:10:13,210
[Xu Miyu]

159
00:10:13,400 --> 00:10:14,510
I'm already off work.

160
00:10:14,510 --> 00:10:15,770
I'm outside right now.

161
00:10:15,800 --> 00:10:16,860
What's the matter?

162
00:10:21,300 --> 00:10:22,540
Where are you going?

163
00:10:22,660 --> 00:10:24,090
[Release to send]

164
00:10:26,910 --> 00:10:27,110
[Release to cancel]

165
00:10:27,150 --> 00:10:28,150
[Xu Miyu]

166
00:10:43,870 --> 00:10:45,250
Ask someone from your department

167
00:10:45,250 --> 00:10:47,710
to come to my office
and fetch the documents.

168
00:10:49,550 --> 00:10:52,310
Okay.
I'll send someone over there right away.

169
00:11:08,210 --> 00:11:15,950
[TAN's Art]

170
00:11:26,790 --> 00:11:28,650
I just had a feeling you'd be here.

171
00:11:28,770 --> 00:11:29,720
Welcome.

172
00:11:29,750 --> 00:11:32,200
I missed your opening ceremony previously,

173
00:11:32,200 --> 00:11:33,890
so I didn't get to tell you—

174
00:11:33,920 --> 00:11:34,790
Congratulations!

175
00:11:34,790 --> 00:11:36,730
You finally have your own gallery.

176
00:11:36,760 --> 00:11:38,140
Alright. Don't stand on ceremony.

177
00:11:38,140 --> 00:11:38,780
Come on in.

178
00:11:39,970 --> 00:11:44,580
[TAN's Art]

179
00:11:52,640 --> 00:11:53,720
Just make a comment.

180
00:11:53,720 --> 00:11:54,760
What do you think?

181
00:11:57,020 --> 00:11:58,620
This is your style,

182
00:11:58,680 --> 00:12:01,150
being both free and bold.

183
00:12:01,910 --> 00:12:03,480
Alright. You still know me the best.

184
00:12:03,480 --> 00:12:04,010
Let's go.

185
00:12:09,780 --> 00:12:11,510
The downstairs is your gallery

186
00:12:11,550 --> 00:12:13,910
while the upstairs is your studio.

187
00:12:15,480 --> 00:12:16,670
When I'm free,

188
00:12:16,670 --> 00:12:17,960
I often visit galleries

189
00:12:17,960 --> 00:12:19,600
and art museums,

190
00:12:19,620 --> 00:12:21,000
but I rarely have the chance

191
00:12:21,000 --> 00:12:23,650
to see an artist's studio
with my own eyes.

192
00:12:23,680 --> 00:12:25,910
Today,
it's like making my dream come true.

193
00:12:25,910 --> 00:12:27,310
Feel free to look around.

194
00:12:31,360 --> 00:12:32,820
Can I touch these?

195
00:12:32,940 --> 00:12:35,670
As long as you don't mind,
feel free to touch them.

196
00:12:40,080 --> 00:12:41,570
The paint is still wet.

197
00:12:44,770 --> 00:12:45,930
What is this?

198
00:12:45,960 --> 00:12:48,440
Is it a work you're trying to creat?

199
00:12:50,490 --> 00:12:51,420
Sort of.

200
00:12:52,720 --> 00:12:54,000
May I have the honor

201
00:12:54,030 --> 00:12:55,360
to be its first viewer?

202
00:12:59,400 --> 00:13:00,200
I'm sorry.

203
00:13:00,200 --> 00:13:00,960
If it's inconvenient...

204
00:13:00,960 --> 00:13:01,760
You can see it.

205
00:13:05,440 --> 00:13:06,440
Okay. Alright.

206
00:13:47,590 --> 00:13:48,700
I originally wanted to

207
00:13:48,700 --> 00:13:51,480
frame it before giving it to you.

208
00:13:51,750 --> 00:13:52,630
Now that...

209
00:13:54,270 --> 00:13:55,080
Okay.

210
00:13:55,480 --> 00:13:56,690
Mr. Tan, I...

211
00:13:56,710 --> 00:13:58,240
Please don't have any pressure.

212
00:13:58,240 --> 00:14:00,240
You helped me
organize the art exhibition so well.

213
00:14:00,240 --> 00:14:02,040
Consider this a thank-you gift.

214
00:14:02,200 --> 00:14:03,660
It's sincere enough, huh?

215
00:14:09,260 --> 00:14:10,200
Thank you.

216
00:14:10,960 --> 00:14:12,690
I like this painting very much.

217
00:14:13,730 --> 00:14:16,130
Actually,
I should be the one thanking you.

218
00:14:17,350 --> 00:14:18,920
Every creator

219
00:14:18,940 --> 00:14:21,670
longs for someone
who can naturally inspire him.

220
00:14:22,200 --> 00:14:23,320
Having met you

221
00:14:24,320 --> 00:14:25,730
is actually my luck.

222
00:14:50,910 --> 00:14:52,910
The Golden Wutong District

223
00:14:53,140 --> 00:14:55,230
is the core area of culture and art.

224
00:14:55,410 --> 00:14:57,540
It suits your temperament perfectly.

225
00:14:57,820 --> 00:15:00,310
Things will definitely
get better and better here.

226
00:15:00,310 --> 00:15:01,710
I'm really happy for you.

227
00:15:03,590 --> 00:15:05,200
Why don't you ask me

228
00:15:05,220 --> 00:15:08,150
why I'm staying in Shanghai
for future development?

229
00:15:12,620 --> 00:15:15,610
This is an ideal place for creators.

230
00:15:17,100 --> 00:15:18,090
Well said.

231
00:15:23,120 --> 00:15:26,900
♪ Love is truly not easy to obtain ♪

232
00:15:23,230 --> 00:15:24,760
The more I look at this city,

233
00:15:24,870 --> 00:15:26,080
the more I like it.

234
00:15:28,350 --> 00:15:29,050
Really.

235
00:15:30,500 --> 00:15:34,200
♪ I can't hold on to you
if you want to leave ♪

236
00:15:37,470 --> 00:15:41,430
♪ I tell myself I'm not hurt
once things settle down ♪

237
00:15:45,110 --> 00:15:49,010
♪ But I realize I can't deceive myself ♪

238
00:15:52,470 --> 00:15:56,220
♪ But I've already started living
like I'm not myself anymore ♪

239
00:15:59,900 --> 00:16:02,780
♪ I feel reluctant ♪

240
00:16:06,120 --> 00:16:11,970
♪ I feel reluctant to recall
or forget those memories ♪

241
00:16:14,460 --> 00:16:17,690
♪ I feel reluctant ♪

242
00:16:21,070 --> 00:16:26,790
♪ I feel reluctant to grab on to you,
and I can't breathe ♪

243
00:16:27,970 --> 00:16:30,830
♪ I've been indulging myself ♪

244
00:16:30,930 --> 00:16:36,050
[My Dear Pearl]

245
00:16:51,860 --> 00:16:53,500
[Yuntian Group,
China Resources Financial Building]

246
00:16:53,520 --> 00:16:54,750
[Project Bidding Meeting]

247
00:16:54,890 --> 00:16:55,740
[China Resources Financial Building,
A Landmark in the City]

248
00:16:55,770 --> 00:16:56,800
[Yuntian Group Invites You
to Build Brilliance Together]

249
00:16:56,900 --> 00:17:00,240
[Fengze Construction]

250
00:17:00,330 --> 00:17:01,220
[Bocheng Construction]

251
00:17:08,540 --> 00:17:09,520
[Xingyao Construction] [Liberty Group]

252
00:17:17,920 --> 00:17:19,750
Hello, Mr. Ji.

253
00:17:20,910 --> 00:17:22,079
Hello, Mr. Ji.

254
00:17:22,640 --> 00:17:23,740
Hello, Mr. Ji.

255
00:17:43,370 --> 00:17:45,090
Welcome, Mr. Lin.

256
00:17:45,120 --> 00:17:46,770
I'm Ji Feng, the general manager here.

257
00:17:46,770 --> 00:17:47,280
Please come in.

258
00:17:47,280 --> 00:17:47,660
Okay.

259
00:17:50,580 --> 00:17:51,370
Hello, everyone.

260
00:17:51,370 --> 00:17:53,380
This way, please.

261
00:17:53,620 --> 00:17:54,350
Hello.

262
00:17:54,380 --> 00:17:55,020
Please come in.

263
00:17:55,020 --> 00:17:56,220
So this is your hotel?

264
00:17:56,640 --> 00:17:57,220
Yes.

265
00:18:07,560 --> 00:18:08,690
Thanks, Wei.

266
00:18:09,660 --> 00:18:11,240
Alright. See you later then.

267
00:18:11,240 --> 00:18:12,350
Okay.

268
00:18:13,480 --> 00:18:14,000
See you later.

269
00:18:14,000 --> 00:18:14,860
Hello, Mr. Wei.

270
00:18:33,060 --> 00:18:33,830
Hello.

271
00:18:33,860 --> 00:18:35,070
Ms. Xu, please come in.

272
00:18:35,070 --> 00:18:36,030
Okay. Thanks.

273
00:18:39,440 --> 00:18:40,640
Mr. Yang.

274
00:18:42,290 --> 00:18:43,530
Ms. Xu.

275
00:18:43,640 --> 00:18:44,680
We've met again.

276
00:18:45,570 --> 00:18:47,130
I've heard this time,

277
00:18:47,160 --> 00:18:48,310
you are already

278
00:18:48,340 --> 00:18:49,540
the sales manager.

279
00:18:49,680 --> 00:18:50,370
Yes.

280
00:18:50,980 --> 00:18:51,940
Congratulations.

281
00:18:51,940 --> 00:18:52,590
Thank you.

282
00:18:53,240 --> 00:18:55,160
Welcome back to Purong Hotel,

283
00:18:55,180 --> 00:18:57,700
and welcome to the bidding meeting.

284
00:18:57,730 --> 00:18:58,990
On behalf of the sales department,

285
00:18:58,990 --> 00:19:00,150
I'm giving this small gift to you.

286
00:19:00,150 --> 00:19:01,790
It's nothing much, but please accept it.

287
00:19:01,790 --> 00:19:02,870
Thank you.

288
00:19:04,050 --> 00:19:05,380
The food is ready.

289
00:19:05,410 --> 00:19:07,160
I'll take you to the Chinese Restaurant
for a meal.

290
00:19:07,160 --> 00:19:08,150
That's great.

291
00:19:08,180 --> 00:19:10,340
I really miss the food at Purong.

292
00:19:10,670 --> 00:19:11,310
Wait a moment for me.

293
00:19:11,310 --> 00:19:12,160
I'm going to get changed.

294
00:19:12,160 --> 00:19:13,620
I'll wait for you outside.

295
00:19:48,690 --> 00:19:49,650
Wait!

296
00:19:55,820 --> 00:19:56,990
Ms. Xu.

297
00:19:57,670 --> 00:19:58,650
You must be a newcomer.

298
00:19:58,650 --> 00:19:59,720
I've never seen you before.

299
00:19:59,720 --> 00:20:00,970
My name is Dai Hui.

300
00:20:01,290 --> 00:20:02,360
Don't be nervous.

301
00:20:02,380 --> 00:20:04,060
Everyone tends to make mistakes at first.

302
00:20:04,060 --> 00:20:04,690
It's fine.

303
00:20:05,910 --> 00:20:06,920
Have a candy.

304
00:20:06,950 --> 00:20:08,280
Thank you, Ms. Xu.

305
00:20:08,850 --> 00:20:09,640
Ms. Xu.

306
00:20:10,520 --> 00:20:11,570
Sorry to keep you waiting.

307
00:20:11,570 --> 00:20:12,250
This way, please.

308
00:20:12,250 --> 00:20:13,030
Let's go.

309
00:20:22,300 --> 00:20:23,310
I'm sorry, Mr. Marcos.

310
00:20:23,310 --> 00:20:25,440
It's fine, Ms. Xu. Just leave it there.

311
00:20:25,550 --> 00:20:27,320
Although I'm allergic to pollen,

312
00:20:27,320 --> 00:20:29,340
I'll be fine in a spacious place like this

313
00:20:29,340 --> 00:20:30,770
for a short while.

314
00:20:30,930 --> 00:20:31,580
But...

315
00:20:31,610 --> 00:20:32,330
It's fine.

316
00:20:33,070 --> 00:20:35,670
I usually can't have flowers in my room,

317
00:20:36,000 --> 00:20:36,720
so,

318
00:20:37,030 --> 00:20:39,970
occasionally seeing them outside
puts me in a good mood.

319
00:20:39,970 --> 00:20:41,720
What's more, don't deprive everyone

320
00:20:41,720 --> 00:20:44,320
of the chance to see flowers
just because of me.

321
00:20:45,220 --> 00:20:46,380
How about this?

322
00:20:46,410 --> 00:20:47,880
Later, I'll put some silk flowers

323
00:20:47,880 --> 00:20:49,080
in your room.

324
00:20:49,220 --> 00:20:51,090
That would be great. Thank you.

325
00:20:51,110 --> 00:20:52,020
Please.

326
00:20:55,090 --> 00:20:55,650
Please.

327
00:20:57,820 --> 00:20:58,670
Wait!

328
00:21:01,700 --> 00:21:02,460
Boss.

329
00:21:05,170 --> 00:21:06,650
Isn't this Mr. Marcos

330
00:21:06,680 --> 00:21:08,010
from the Liberty Group?

331
00:21:09,370 --> 00:21:10,340
Hello.

332
00:21:24,460 --> 00:21:25,630
Mr. Niu, this way, please.

333
00:21:25,630 --> 00:21:26,190
Okay.

334
00:21:27,550 --> 00:21:28,360
See you later.

335
00:21:31,850 --> 00:21:32,840
Please come in.

336
00:21:36,100 --> 00:21:36,810
Thank you.

337
00:21:39,850 --> 00:21:40,930
Give it to me.

338
00:21:41,560 --> 00:21:42,550
His assistant seems to be

339
00:21:42,550 --> 00:21:44,880
someone who left our company previously.

340
00:21:47,480 --> 00:21:48,270
Marcos,

341
00:21:48,270 --> 00:21:50,330
is there anything I can help you with?

342
00:21:51,060 --> 00:21:52,130
Well,

343
00:21:52,150 --> 00:21:54,110
the assistant to the president
of Jinkun Group

344
00:21:54,110 --> 00:21:56,650
came from our company.

345
00:21:57,210 --> 00:21:58,160
Three years ago,

346
00:21:58,160 --> 00:21:59,400
he was fired

347
00:21:59,400 --> 00:22:01,000
due to some misconduct.

348
00:22:01,450 --> 00:22:02,660
Maybe we're judging

349
00:22:02,680 --> 00:22:05,010
others by our own standards improperly.

350
00:22:05,040 --> 00:22:07,120
Also, Jinkun Group's reputation

351
00:22:07,140 --> 00:22:09,200
in the industry is quite divided.

352
00:22:09,220 --> 00:22:10,380
Now that I've run into him today,

353
00:22:10,380 --> 00:22:11,140
I just

354
00:22:11,620 --> 00:22:12,880
have to keep an eye out.

355
00:22:12,900 --> 00:22:13,880
Don't worry.

356
00:22:13,900 --> 00:22:15,280
I will tell all departments

357
00:22:15,280 --> 00:22:17,000
to strengthen the measures
on information security management.

358
00:22:17,000 --> 00:22:18,490
I really appreciate your help.

359
00:22:18,490 --> 00:22:19,290
Thank you.

360
00:22:29,200 --> 00:22:31,330
Are you sure you really want to do this?

361
00:22:31,510 --> 00:22:33,940
This is what we agreed on
from the very beginning.

362
00:22:33,940 --> 00:22:35,620
My demands are quite simple.

363
00:22:35,650 --> 00:22:37,560
Either you help me
find out about the base price,

364
00:22:37,560 --> 00:22:38,280
or

365
00:22:38,310 --> 00:22:39,170
you help me find out about

366
00:22:39,170 --> 00:22:40,830
Liberty Group's bid price.

367
00:22:41,290 --> 00:22:43,800
Well, how can this work?

368
00:22:46,060 --> 00:22:47,160
Why didn't you knock on the door
before coming in?

369
00:22:47,160 --> 00:22:48,070
How rude.

370
00:22:48,250 --> 00:22:49,210
I'm sorry, Mr. Wei.

371
00:22:49,210 --> 00:22:49,970
Just get out.

372
00:22:55,460 --> 00:22:57,130
As the saying goes,

373
00:22:57,150 --> 00:22:59,350
"Great wealth comes with great risks."

374
00:22:59,920 --> 00:23:01,850
As long as you put this small device

375
00:23:01,900 --> 00:23:04,300
in Marcos' room secretly,

376
00:23:04,320 --> 00:23:05,780
by doing it just like that,

377
00:23:06,430 --> 00:23:08,290
you'll get 5 million yuan easily.

378
00:23:08,300 --> 00:23:09,020
Bro,

379
00:23:09,400 --> 00:23:10,600
I treat you well, don't I?

380
00:23:10,600 --> 00:23:11,820
Mr. Niu,

381
00:23:11,850 --> 00:23:13,850
this is not a small matter.

382
00:23:13,990 --> 00:23:15,340
The bidding meeting for the skyscraper

383
00:23:15,340 --> 00:23:16,790
involves funds of billions of yuan.

384
00:23:16,790 --> 00:23:17,720
The risk I'm taking

385
00:23:17,720 --> 00:23:19,920
does not match up with the reward.

386
00:23:20,240 --> 00:23:21,810
What are you talking about?

387
00:23:23,000 --> 00:23:24,720
This grand hotel is yours.

388
00:23:24,960 --> 00:23:26,420
These are all your people.

389
00:23:27,000 --> 00:23:29,060
What risks will you even have to take?

390
00:23:29,930 --> 00:23:32,190
Don't you know my current situation?

391
00:23:32,280 --> 00:23:33,480
That old madam above me

392
00:23:33,480 --> 00:23:35,450
won't tolerate any misconduct.

393
00:23:35,710 --> 00:23:37,240
An ambitious guy
has also come from outside,

394
00:23:37,240 --> 00:23:38,530
trying to overthrow me.

395
00:23:38,530 --> 00:23:40,690
I have an insatiable wife at home, too.

396
00:23:40,950 --> 00:23:44,350
How long can I live on the 5 million yuan
you're offering to me?

397
00:23:47,460 --> 00:23:48,660
Then give me a number.

398
00:23:51,440 --> 00:23:52,570
20 million yuan.

399
00:23:52,800 --> 00:23:54,360
Pay 10% of it first.

400
00:23:56,510 --> 00:23:58,510
You haven't done anything yet,

401
00:23:58,510 --> 00:23:59,900
and you're asking me for 2 million yuan?

402
00:23:59,900 --> 00:24:00,720
On what grounds can you do that,

403
00:24:00,720 --> 00:24:01,550
dude?

404
00:24:02,650 --> 00:24:04,260
Because we're friends.

405
00:24:05,430 --> 00:24:07,150
You wouldn't just use me, your buddy,

406
00:24:07,150 --> 00:24:08,810
like a credit card, would you?

407
00:24:10,170 --> 00:24:11,720
If you don't want to do that,
just forget it.

408
00:24:11,720 --> 00:24:13,130
Just pretend I didn't say it.

409
00:24:13,130 --> 00:24:14,610
Let's eat. It tastes good.

410
00:24:14,640 --> 00:24:15,510
Come on.

411
00:24:16,750 --> 00:24:17,550
Deal.

412
00:24:21,380 --> 00:24:23,300
That's more like it, Mr. Niu.

413
00:24:23,330 --> 00:24:25,120
Come on. Cheers.

414
00:24:25,150 --> 00:24:26,610
You're really something.

415
00:24:31,980 --> 00:24:32,930
Eat.

416
00:24:33,310 --> 00:24:41,770
[Director's Office]

417
00:24:33,720 --> 00:24:34,790
Don't you think

418
00:24:34,790 --> 00:24:36,990
we need to change our mindset this time?

419
00:24:41,240 --> 00:24:41,720
As for the fact that

420
00:24:41,720 --> 00:24:43,480
Yuntian Group's bidding meeting

421
00:24:43,480 --> 00:24:45,150
can be held at Purong this time,

422
00:24:45,150 --> 00:24:47,400
I think it's all thanks to Ms. Xu.

423
00:24:47,420 --> 00:24:49,660
She is indeed a rare talent.

424
00:24:49,960 --> 00:24:52,960
I'm wondering if we could promote her

425
00:24:52,960 --> 00:24:54,020
to be my aide later.

426
00:24:54,040 --> 00:24:55,510
I believe next year's sales volume

427
00:24:55,510 --> 00:24:57,510
will reach new heights.

428
00:24:57,960 --> 00:25:00,160
Actually, Mr. Ji has the same plan, too.

429
00:25:00,170 --> 00:25:02,130
The HR department
has already been informed.

430
00:25:02,130 --> 00:25:04,700
After this bidding
is conducted successfully,

431
00:25:04,700 --> 00:25:07,330
the sales department
will be entrusted to you two.

432
00:25:07,330 --> 00:25:07,980
Okay.

433
00:25:10,060 --> 00:25:12,600
[Director's Office]

434
00:25:15,150 --> 00:25:22,220
[Purong Hotel]

435
00:25:15,420 --> 00:25:16,620
I know what I'm doing.

436
00:25:17,920 --> 00:25:19,250
I'll contact you later.

437
00:25:20,240 --> 00:25:22,770
Mr. Wei,
I need to discuss something with you.

438
00:25:23,830 --> 00:25:24,550
What is it?

439
00:25:24,550 --> 00:25:25,770
Think of a way quickly

440
00:25:25,790 --> 00:25:28,650
to help me drive Xu Miyu
out of the sales department.

441
00:25:29,100 --> 00:25:30,580
Why are you suddenly saying this?

442
00:25:30,580 --> 00:25:32,370
I've been promoted to this position
for just a few days.

443
00:25:32,370 --> 00:25:34,820
She has already teamed up
with the new director

444
00:25:34,820 --> 00:25:37,020
and tried every possible means
to undermine me.

445
00:25:37,020 --> 00:25:38,960
They want to use the performance
of this bidding meeting

446
00:25:38,960 --> 00:25:40,270
to edge me out of my position

447
00:25:40,270 --> 00:25:41,190
as vice director.

448
00:25:41,190 --> 00:25:42,740
This is not like your style.

449
00:25:43,350 --> 00:25:45,460
If you sit firmly in your position,

450
00:25:45,490 --> 00:25:47,150
can anyone remove you from it?

451
00:25:47,440 --> 00:25:48,960
Anyway, if I get edged out,

452
00:25:48,980 --> 00:25:51,240
then no one can help you with your things.

453
00:25:52,790 --> 00:25:53,700
Zhenzhen.

454
00:25:54,720 --> 00:25:56,640
You need to be more understanding.

455
00:25:56,640 --> 00:25:59,350
Ji Feng is now competing with me
in the sales department.

456
00:25:59,350 --> 00:26:01,520
It's inevitable
that these things will happen.

457
00:26:01,520 --> 00:26:02,800
Just put up with it.

458
00:26:03,030 --> 00:26:05,130
There will be more opportunities later,
won't there?

459
00:26:05,130 --> 00:26:06,160
Besides, I'm not anxious yet,

460
00:26:06,160 --> 00:26:07,820
so what are you anxious about?

461
00:26:08,100 --> 00:26:09,310
Wei Siyuan.

462
00:26:09,420 --> 00:26:12,330
You always make your statement
sound so nice every time,

463
00:26:12,330 --> 00:26:15,060
but you've never
fulfilled any of your promises.

464
00:26:15,360 --> 00:26:17,360
My patience is limited.

465
00:26:29,130 --> 00:26:29,940
Wait a moment.

466
00:26:56,570 --> 00:26:57,550
Find a way

467
00:26:57,550 --> 00:26:58,310
to put this stuff

468
00:26:58,310 --> 00:27:00,460
in the room of the Liberty Group's boss.

469
00:27:00,460 --> 00:27:02,000
If you get this done,

470
00:27:02,810 --> 00:27:04,190
I will give you 5 million yuan.

471
00:27:04,190 --> 00:27:06,190
Also, I will promote you

472
00:27:06,230 --> 00:27:07,640
to director officially.

473
00:27:08,010 --> 00:27:09,010
What do you think?

474
00:27:13,830 --> 00:27:14,790
The business
discussed at this bidding meeting

475
00:27:14,790 --> 00:27:16,130
is worth hundreds of millions of yuan.

476
00:27:16,130 --> 00:27:17,930
Doing this is too risky.

477
00:27:18,200 --> 00:27:19,660
I might be put into prison.

478
00:27:20,330 --> 00:27:21,290
Zhenzhen.

479
00:27:22,130 --> 00:27:24,390
Since when have you become such a coward?

480
00:27:24,840 --> 00:27:27,380
High risks bring high rewards.

481
00:27:27,680 --> 00:27:29,340
Don't you want your benefits?

482
00:27:29,490 --> 00:27:31,220
Don't you have a child to raise?

483
00:27:35,870 --> 00:27:37,110
Wei Siyuan.

484
00:27:37,920 --> 00:27:39,190
You've long made up your mind

485
00:27:39,190 --> 00:27:41,060
to ask me to do this for you.

486
00:27:41,510 --> 00:27:42,640
Honestly speaking,

487
00:27:43,570 --> 00:27:44,730
I can't trust

488
00:27:44,750 --> 00:27:46,800
or rely on anyone else.

489
00:27:47,610 --> 00:27:48,740
It has to be you only.

490
00:27:53,180 --> 00:27:53,940
Okay.

491
00:27:54,780 --> 00:27:56,010
For my child's sake,

492
00:27:56,300 --> 00:27:58,830
I can help you
plant the listening device there.

493
00:27:58,830 --> 00:28:00,220
But I have a condition.

494
00:28:00,860 --> 00:28:02,610
5 million yuan is too little.

495
00:28:03,370 --> 00:28:05,160
I want 8 million yuan.

496
00:28:05,290 --> 00:28:07,820
I want to be paid
immediately after it's done.

497
00:28:12,310 --> 00:28:13,440
This is more like you,

498
00:28:13,440 --> 00:28:14,720
Lu Zhenzhen.

499
00:28:15,070 --> 00:28:16,140
8 million yuan.

500
00:28:16,920 --> 00:28:17,530
Okay.

501
00:28:18,110 --> 00:28:20,430
I'll just give you 8 million yuan. Deal.

502
00:28:46,960 --> 00:28:48,050
Here you are.

503
00:28:48,910 --> 00:28:49,970
Ms. Xu.

504
00:28:50,090 --> 00:28:52,420
Are you going to
give these to the clients?

505
00:28:52,590 --> 00:28:53,920
These are prepared for the guests

506
00:28:53,920 --> 00:28:54,790
who attend the bidding meeting.

507
00:28:54,790 --> 00:28:56,530
I'll deliver them to their rooms later.

508
00:28:56,530 --> 00:28:58,000
Do you need my help?

509
00:28:58,020 --> 00:28:59,760
It's fine. I can go by myself.

510
00:28:59,790 --> 00:29:00,580
Okay.

511
00:29:17,160 --> 00:29:18,360
Miyu.

512
00:29:18,610 --> 00:29:19,760
Why are you here?

513
00:29:20,580 --> 00:29:22,130
I'm here to deliver something to Mr. Yang.

514
00:29:22,130 --> 00:29:22,830
Is he in his room?

515
00:29:22,830 --> 00:29:25,030
I just saw him go out with his assistant.

516
00:29:25,480 --> 00:29:27,810
Well...
I'll wait here for him for a while.

517
00:29:28,460 --> 00:29:29,720
He just went out a moment ago.

518
00:29:29,720 --> 00:29:31,300
I also don't know when he'll be back.

519
00:29:31,300 --> 00:29:32,530
Let me open the door for you first.

520
00:29:32,530 --> 00:29:34,360
You're delivering something
to the guest anyway.

521
00:29:34,360 --> 00:29:34,970
Thank you.

522
00:29:37,880 --> 00:29:38,960
Ms. Xu, Xiang.

523
00:29:38,990 --> 00:29:40,600
This guest needs to check in.

524
00:29:41,600 --> 00:29:43,010
Then how about going by yourself?

525
00:29:43,010 --> 00:29:44,700
Just return the room card to me later.

526
00:29:44,700 --> 00:29:46,230
I'll be back in two minutes.

527
00:29:46,510 --> 00:29:48,770
Come this way
and let me help you check in.

528
00:29:51,110 --> 00:29:52,500
Please show your ID.

529
00:29:57,090 --> 00:29:57,810
Dai.

530
00:29:58,400 --> 00:29:59,230
Ms. Xu.

531
00:29:59,550 --> 00:30:00,700
Why are you here?

532
00:30:00,830 --> 00:30:01,790
I need to go to Room 1822

533
00:30:01,790 --> 00:30:03,050
to deliver something.

534
00:30:03,200 --> 00:30:03,930
Are you okay?

535
00:30:04,280 --> 00:30:04,810
I'm fine.

536
00:30:04,850 --> 00:30:06,090
I'll pick them up with you together.

537
00:30:06,090 --> 00:30:07,090
Thank you, Ms. Xu.

538
00:30:58,500 --> 00:31:00,480
[Purong Hotel Staff Apartment]

539
00:31:05,790 --> 00:31:06,510
M-Miyu.

540
00:31:06,510 --> 00:31:07,590
You're back.

541
00:31:10,960 --> 00:31:12,000
Why are you here?

542
00:31:13,170 --> 00:31:13,890
Well,

543
00:31:13,920 --> 00:31:15,110
I've brought you some

544
00:31:15,110 --> 00:31:16,750
hometown specialities.

545
00:31:16,750 --> 00:31:18,330
Mom and Dad
asked me to bring them here for you.

546
00:31:18,330 --> 00:31:20,290
Look. There's also your favorite

547
00:31:20,320 --> 00:31:21,480
dried fish here.

548
00:31:27,800 --> 00:31:28,630
Um...

549
00:31:30,250 --> 00:31:32,720
I had a bad attitude last time.

550
00:31:33,170 --> 00:31:34,580
I'm sorry.

551
00:31:34,610 --> 00:31:36,850
Mom and Dad scolded me when I went back.

552
00:31:37,790 --> 00:31:39,460
Actually, I came here this time

553
00:31:39,460 --> 00:31:42,180
just to sincerely apologize to you.

554
00:31:42,830 --> 00:31:43,790
Really, Miyu.

555
00:31:46,250 --> 00:31:47,490
It's my fault.

556
00:31:52,160 --> 00:31:54,970
I've quit my job in Shanghai, too.

557
00:31:58,310 --> 00:31:59,160
Well,

558
00:31:59,570 --> 00:32:01,920
Mom and Dad are getting older,
aren't they?

559
00:32:01,920 --> 00:32:03,380
I just want to go back

560
00:32:03,400 --> 00:32:05,680
and help them with the guesthouse.

561
00:32:06,780 --> 00:32:09,060
So... What about Man?

562
00:32:09,220 --> 00:32:10,690
Is he still going to
the international school?

563
00:32:10,690 --> 00:32:11,650
No.

564
